713645f-a.title: Manhattan: 53rd Street (East) - Madison Avenue
713645f-a.text:
East 53rd Street, north side, east from Madison, to and including
Park Aves.  October 28, 1930.
P. L. Sperr.

713646f-a.title: Manhattan: 53rd Street (East) - Madison Avenue
713646f-a.text:
East 53rd Street, at, adjoining and east of the S.E. corner of Madison
Ave., as seen thru clearance at the N.E. corner. Prominent building
shown under construction, is the General Electric Building.
December 21, 1930.
P. L. Sperr.

721379f-a.title: Manhattan: Madison Avenue - 53rd Street
721379f-a.text:
Madison Ave., east side, north from and including East 53rd Street.
October 28, 1930.
P. L. Sperr.

721377f-a.title: Manhattan: Madison Avenue - 53rd Street
721377f-a.text:
Madison Avenue at N.W. corner of 53rd Street, from S.E. corner.
On the N.E. corner, where a clearing is shown, the new 42-story
International Mart is about to be erected.
December 21, 1930.
P. L. Sperr, Photographer.
